This port translates the algorithm (exp table, unigram^0.75 negative-sampling
table, subsampling, LCG RNG, alpha decay, CBOW & skip-gram negative-sampling
gradient updates) into Swift. It performs all training in memory and does not
read or write files. The reference source is retained at docs/reference-word2vec.c.
